This is HTML5 validation dialect for the Thymeleaf template engine.

2.0.x versions are compatible with Thymeleaf 2.0.x versions, while 2.1.x versions are compatible with Thymeleaf 2.1.x versions. 

If you want to use HTML5 validation dialect in your project, download the latest html5valdialect.jar file.

Maven users can find the library in the Central Repository:
        <dependency>
            <groupId>net.sourceforge.html5val</groupId>
            <artifactId>html5valdialect</artifactId>
            <version>1.0.0-beta3</version>
        </dependency>

If you want to see the library in action, download the html5valdialect-example-webapp.war demo application.

